<title class="- topic/title ">alarm-StationRecipient</title>
<shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">This component manages the transfer of alarms between the <apiname class="+ topic/keyword pr-d/apiname ">AlarmService</apiname> and a remote station. For example, a station
may send alarm notifications to a supervisor station – or any other
remote station in the system. The <apiname class="+ topic/keyword pr-d/apiname ">StationRecipient</apiname> is available in the <wintitle class="+ topic/keyword ui-d/wintitle ">alarm</wintitle> palette.</shortdesc>
