<refbody class="- topic/body        reference/refbody ">
<section class="- topic/section "><p class="- topic/p ">The station recipient component provides a place to specify
the location and other details about that remote station. The properties
on a station recipient include a field for selecting the remote station,
as well as alarm collection options.</p><image href="../graphic/StationRecipient_0000031397.png" placement="break" scale="65" class="- topic/image "/></section>
